The paper discusses a novel text-based question answering task that involves interactive comprehension, which falls under the domain of natural language processing and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes and evaluates deep reinforcement learning agents, which suggests that it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper focuses on human-computer interaction and the challenges of machine reading systems, which could place it under cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). Finally, the paper involves game generation, which could potentially fall under cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
